    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been a reliable daily driver. The engine starts up immediately and runs strong, while the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears without hesitation. It has been well-maintained with regular oil changes and recent brake service. On the exterior, there are a few minor surface scratches and one small door ding consistent with its age, but nothing that affects performance. The interior is clean, though the driver's seat shows some light wear on the bolster. All electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. This is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner.",
