      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road, you've found it! This car has been my trusty companion and is in solid shape, ready for its next adventure. It's been well-loved and runs super smoothly, making it perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love for it to go to a good home. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
