    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and performance. The exterior shines with a deep luster, showing only the minor, honest signs of careful road use\u2014such as tiny stone chips\u2014that you would expect from a car that has been driven with pride. The body lines are straight and the trim is intact. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, and every electronic feature, from the climate control to the infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with a consistent rhythm, backed by a documented service history that confirms its reliability. The transmission shifts seamlessly, providing a comfortable and responsive driving experience whether you are navigating city streets or cruising on the highway. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been cared for by a non-smoker and is ready to provide many more miles of enjoyment.",
      "price": 34800.0,
